      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: \"أَحِبُّوا اَلصِّبْيَانَ وَ اِرْحَمُوهُمْ وَ إِذَا وَعَدْتُمُوهُمْ فَفُوا لَهُمْ فَإِنَّهُمْ لاَ يَرَوْنَ إِلاَّ أَنَّكُمْ تَرْزُقُونَهُمْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4702 - The Prophet (peace and blessings be upon him and his family) said: \"Love the children and have mercy on them. When you promise them something, fulfill it for them, for they only perceive that you are the ones who provide for them.\""
        ]
      }
    },
